post_text:
Please honor our seniors on Tuesday, May 5 by driving through the TVA Credit Union JC Cardinals Parking lot from 8:15-8:35pm. Enter the lot at Legion St., go left following the car line to show your support for our seniors. Wave, say hello, honk but please remain in your cars.

Left to Right Senior Baseball Players with Parents Names:

Landon Slemp, son of Scott Slemp and Debbie Ladd;

Matthew Levi, son of Tom Levi and Kathy Levi;

Caleb Marmo, son of Scott and Kim Marmo;

Hunter Phillips, son of Marty and Heather Phillips;

Gehrig Carcich, son of Jeremy Carcich and Dawn Carcich;

Clayton McKenzie, son of Daniel and DeAnne McKenzie;

Josh Wooten, son of Kim and Betsy Wooten

